headline: Elevance Health Foundation Announces New Five-Year, $150 Million Commitment
summary: INDIANAPOLIS - Elevance Health Foundation today announces its new five-year, $150 million commitment aimed at addressing the physical, behavioral, and social needs of under-resourced communities....
